quran[7{c,v,t}:
9,62,momino! yeh log tumahray samnay khuda ki kasmain khatay hain taakay tum ko khush kar den. halaank agar yeh ( dil se ) momin hotay to khuda aur is ke paighambar khush karne ke ziyada mustahiq hain
9,63,kiya un logon ko maloom nahi ke jo shakhs khuda aur is ke rasool se muqaabla karta hai to is ke liye jahannum ki aag ( tayyar ) hai jis mein woh hamesha ( jalta ) rahay ga. yeh barri ruswai hai
9,64,munhafiq drtay rehtay hain ke un ( ke paighambar ) par kahin koi aisi sourat ( nah ) utar aeye ke un ke dil ki baton ko un ( musalmanoon ) par zahir kar day. keh do ke hansi kiye jao. jis baat se tum drtay ho khuda is ko zaroor zahir kardey ga
9,65,aur agar tum un se ( is baray mein ) daryaft karo to kahin ge hum to yun hi baat cheet aur dil lagi karte they. kahokiya tum khuda aur is ki ayaton aur is ke rasool se hansi karte they
9,66,bahanay mat banaao tum imaan laane ke baad kafir ho chuke ho. agar hum tum mein se aik jamaat ko maaf kar dein to doosri jamaat ko saza bhi den ge kyunkay woh gunah karte rahay hain
9,67,munhafiq mard aur munhafiq aurtain aik dosray ke hum jins ( yani aik terhan ke ) hain ke buray kaam karne ko kehte aur naik kamon se mana karte aur ( kharch karne se ) haath band kiye rehtay hain. unhon ne khuda ko bhala diya to khuda ne un ko bhala diya. be shak munhafiq nafarman hain
9,68,allah ne munhafiq mardon aur munhafiq aurton aur kafiroon se aatish jahannum ka wadakiya hai jis mein hamesha ( jaltay ) rahen ge. wohi un ke Laiq hai. aur khuda ne un par laanat kar di hai. aur un ke liye hamesha ka azaab ( tayyar ) hai
